title: Lil Wyte: A Memphis Icon
itunes:title: Lil Wyte: A Memphis Icon
description:
Bunnie is joined by veteran rapper Lil Wyte, a total icon that made his way from Memphis to stages all over the world. In Part 1, he talks about his developing bromance with Jelly, the secrets behind his early freestyling, what made his Mrs. Wyte stand out and got him to settle down, Three 6 Mafia, and the guardian angels that help guide him along. 

Lil Wyte: YouTube | IG | Spotify 

Bunnie: TikTok | IG | YouTube
